{"article_id":"HffzfQqnuQBMIqa2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Speaker John A. Boehner said Sunday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he is prepared to let the Department of Homeland Security shut down in less than two weeks","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and that Democrats would be to blame .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"\" The House has acted .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"We ' ve done our job .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Senate Democrats are the ones","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"putting us in this precarious position , \"","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Boehner said on Fox News Sunday .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"The House passed a bill","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that would keep the Homeland Security Department running ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but defunds the president ' s executive amnesty","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"many Republicans said","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"was an unconstitutional executive overreach .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"The Senate , however , has failed to overcome multiple Democrat-led filibusters","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and doesn ' t look able to pass the House bill .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"With the clock ticking on funding for the Department of Homeland Security ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"which will expire Feb. 27 at midnight ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"the House and Senate left Washington for a weeklong break for President ' s Day .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Boehner said","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Democrats aren ' t even willing to vote","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to begin debate on the bill","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"- an oft-heard criticism from Democrats","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"when they were in the Senate majority","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"trying to overcome Republican-led stalemates last year .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Democrats rejected Mr. Boehner ' s finger of blame","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Americans will realize","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"it is Republicans","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"who are refusing to budge","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and placing the country ' s national security at risk .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" When Speaker Boehner tied immigration to DHS funding ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"he knew exactly what he was doing ;","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"unless I get my way ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"I ' m going to shut down a large part of the government , \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Sen. Charles E. Schumer , New York Democrat , said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"\" To now blame Democrats","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"when members of his own party , conservative leaders and others have all asked him to back off this game of chicken","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"is disingenuous at best . \"","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Senate Republicans said","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that shutting down the Department of Homeland Security","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"- especially at a time","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"when radical Islamic terrorist threats are growing -","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"is not the answer to the president ' s actions .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"\" We do not need to leave our nation in a situation with the types of threats","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"we have","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"with an agency","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that is not working at full steam , \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Sen. Bob Corker , Tennessee Republican and chairman of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee , said on the CBS program \" Face the Nation . \"","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Sen. John McCain , Arizona Republican , said","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Americans elected a GOP majority to both chambers of Congress","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"to get things done ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"not to have infighting between House and Senate Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"\" We can not cut funding from the Department of Homeland Security .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"We need to sit down","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and work this thing out , \"","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he said on \" Meet the Press. \"","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"\" There ' s ways","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"we can address what the president did was unconstitutional ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"but it ' s not through shutting down the Department of Homeland Security ;","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"it ' s too serious . \"","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Mr. Boehner said","depth":3},{"id":63,"text":"the House will not vote on another bill","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that is able to pass the Senate","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"and that the responsibility is on senators to come up with a plan","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"if they are unable to move the House-passed bill .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"\" If the Senate doesn ' t like it ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"they ' ll have to produce something","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that fits their institution , \"","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"The speaker said","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"it ' s imperative to rein in what many Republicans believe was an executive overreach","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"when Mr. Obama issued an immigration executive order last year .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"\" The Congress just can ' t sit by","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"and watch the president defy the Constitution , \"","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"\" So the House acted .","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"Now it ' s time","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"for the Senate to act . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":141,"right":158,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":87,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":82,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":0,"right":81,"r